verseObjects.content: + \ft In place of \fq our joy,\fq* some ancient manuscripts read\fqa your joy.\fqa*
+ \ft Some ancient manuscripts read, \fqa and you know all things.\fqa*
+ \ft Some older versions leave out \fq and we are.\fq*

+ \ft Some ancient manuscripts read, \fqa and every spirit that does not acknowledge that Jesus has come in the flesh is not from God. This is the spirit of the antichrist, which you have heard is coming, and now is already in the world.\fqa*
+ \ft Some older versions read, \fqa For there are three that bear witness in heaven:\fqa* However, the best copies do not have this reading.

+ \ft Some older versions read, \fqa the Father, the Word, and the Holy Spirit. These three are one; and there are three that bear witness on earth: the Spirit, the water, and the blood; and these three are as one.\fqa* However, the best copies do not have this reading.
